plot: Crocker seeks out a new source of magic from Timmy's house. Realizing it's Sparky, Crocker tries to turn him against Timmy.Crocker grades on a bell curve so Timmy wishes everyone was dumber than him.
title: "The Fairly OddParents" Turner & Pooch/Dumbbell Curve
